Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.block.web

Class Summary
SOAPInvoke Invoke a remote procedure call given by the name and emit the response.
SOAPReceive Listen for a SOAP message as the given endpoint and return the submitted value along with the information where to respond to this message.
SOAPRespond Send a response message to the given target and indicate when it completed.
SOAPSend Send an object via a SOAP message to the given endpoint.
WebGET Issue a GET request to the given datasource and return the response value.
WebPOST Issue a POST request to the given datasource and return the response.
WebReceive R eceive a GET/POST message along with the information where to send the response.
WebRespond Respond with the given string and indicate when it completes.
